392. Telegram From the Department of State to the Mission to the
                            United NationsSource:
                                Department of State, Central Files, 770G.00/12–3062. Secret;
                                Priority. Drafted by Sisco;
                                cleared in substance by Williams, Kaysen, McGhee, and Ball; and approved by Cleveland. Repeated to London, Léopoldville,
                                Brussels, and Elisabethville.
